title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - Ib w/ Grey Waste Tim
description:
With guest Grey Waste Tim we discuss the biggest power in the Shivering Sea: Ibben. From the fall of their God-Kings, wars with Sarnor and the Dothraki, and exploring regions that Westeros knows little to nothing of, there's a lot to say about these secretive yet frequently seen people. Included are discussions on the influence of Tolkien, Lovecraft and IRL Neanderthals.
